<table><tr><td>National Clinical Guideline Centre. Obesity: identification, assessment and management of overweight and obesity in children, young people and adults. London (UK): National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE); 2014 Nov. 64 p.&nbsp;(Clinical guideline; no. 189).&nbsp;</td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712203901/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=48872&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=http%253a%252f%252fwww.nice.org.uk%252fguidance%252fcg189">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712203901im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
