                        <li><a href="/web/20180712203901/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Adult%20%2819%20to%2044%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Adult%2B%2819%2Bto%2B44%2Byears%29">Adult (19 to 44 years)</a></li>                      
                        <li><a href="/web/20180712203901/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Aged%20%2865%20to%2079%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Aged%2B%2865%2Bto%2B79%2Byears%29">Aged (65 to 79 years)</a></li>                      
                        <li><a href="/web/20180712203901/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Aged%2C%2080%20and%20over&amp;fLockTerm=Aged%252c%2B80%2Band%2Bover">Aged, 80 and over</a></li>                      
